**Brocode just got an upgrade. Introducing gpt-5.3-brocode.**

Brocode is now powered by gpt-5.3-brocode, our most capable agentic coding model yet. It's built for long-running, project-scale work, with mid-turn steering + frequent progress updates so you can collaborate while it runs (and it's faster too).

Learn more: https://openai.com/index/introducing-gpt-5-3-brocode/

You can keep using gpt-5.1-brocode if you prefer.
